songs.title: Thugger’s Interlude
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Going under

[Verse]
Tryna keep myself from going under
I've been listening to Young Thugger
When it's good, it's good, but the question is
Are you down to fuck with the other side?
(No cap, no rap cap)
Lately I been bumping trap music
Don't wanna listen if I can’t dab to it
'Cause all that other shit makes me think about
All the things I don't wanna think about
But I'm a hypocrite, 'cause here I am with another slow song
I'm a hypocrite, singing like a nigga doing no wrong
Ever since I got me a check, I got a check
Them digits really have them bitches
Coming for your neck (for your neck)
